{"tid":328924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"等了80年，尼斯湖水怪終上岸，「曬大陽」照成熱話","createTime":"2017-07-20T03:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T03:32:06.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34c7296c59f2a0697157f56757b03313d2631fcc","tid":328924,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國蘇格蘭的尼斯湖水怪傳說有80多年之久，從1933年首次被目擊以來至今，無數探險家到尼斯湖想找到水怪本尊，但全都無功而返。但有外媒報導指出，近來有位蘇格蘭民眾在山丘遛狗時，竟然看到疑似尼斯湖水怪爬上陸地來，照片傳到網路引發各界熱議。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，66歲的瑞特（Jimmy Wright）表示，近日他在蘇格蘭小鎮基爾恩（Killearn）的克羅爾山（Crow Hill）遛狗時，發現了一隻疑似是尼斯湖水怪的生物，他立刻拍下照片，拍完後生物就離開了他的視線，之後他把照片上傳至基爾恩鎮的臉書粉絲專頁，引發鎮民熱烈議論，許多人都認為尼斯湖水怪爬上路地了。<br />\n其中有位鎮民建議大家為這隻生物取名字，目前以「Nessie Dorma」這個名字遙遙領先。但也有很多民眾抱持反對意見，認為這個生物並不是尼斯湖水怪，反而比較像是恐龍，也有人說那只是枯掉的老樹根而已。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2137569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2137569&d=5%2Bt6gKX9MLuhq4I3ofa%2FwZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ab67d5fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2137569&h=cfad88a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2137569</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/112546_e0afc27efc00d6bba7ee0fce2b5e0521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F112546_e0afc27efc00d6bba7ee0fce2b5e0521.jpg&h=23d2ce15&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/112547_f0dbc5751442303c6bbdf89475eafc57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F112547_f0dbc5751442303c6bbdf89475eafc57.jpg&h=3461d592&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94268077b82896cd6b1af273e4715d88f0c16d10","tid":328924,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"明明係棵樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae5a15f792d28806a09b0c0ea3558065810ebc0","tid":328924,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"832c9bee2a8457026b3374d2b64a31eabc0a75a0","tid":328924,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:32:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}